Package edu.uky.cs.nil.sabre

Class Beliefs

java.lang.Object
edu.uky.cs.nil.sabre.Beliefs
All Implemented Interfaces:
State, Serializable
public class Beliefs extends Object implements Serializable, State
A wrapper around any state which represents an character's beliefs in that state. This wrapper simply prepends the character onto every expression it evaluates and then evaluates the expression in the wrapped state.
Author:
Stephen G. Ware
